        "label": "Paragraph 1",
        "default": "Soulolith was born from a deeply personal journey. After years of navigating modern chaos and emotional imbalance, and the search for inner peace, our founder discovered the transformative power of crystals — not as superstition, but as tools for intention and mindfulness."
      },
      {
        "type": "textarea",
        "id": "story_founder_p2",
        "label": "Paragraph 2",
        "default": "What started as a small collection of stones gathered during travels across India became a mission: to share the beauty and energy of authentic crystals with those who are ready to receive them."
      },
      {
        "type": "textarea",
        "id": "story_founder_p3",
        "label": "Paragraph 3",
        "default": "Every piece we create carries the intention it was made with. We believe the stones find their people — and perhaps, this is how you found us."
      }
